Title: Per Manum
Plot: When Scully and Doggett are contacted by a man who claims his wife was murdered shortly after giving birth to an alien baby, Scully digs deeper into reports of alien fertilization on humans, and she begins to question her own pregnancy and its conception.
GuestStars: Adam Baldwin, Victoria Gallegos, Jennifer Griffin, David Purdham, Jay Acovone, Steven Anderson, Megan Follows, Diana Castle, Elizabeth Cheap, Christopher Stanley, Karl T. Wright, Alexandra Margulies, Saxon Traino
